魂之挽歌创造一道魔能。死亡时会自动释放魂之挽歌，不占用主动大招的冷却时间。","dmg":"攻击力:<span class=\"attribVal\">80 / 120 / 160</span>","notes":"根据影魔收集的灵魂数量，每2个灵魂会产生1道伤害波，伤害波数量上限为18道。<br />魂之挽歌的移动速度减缓和攻击力降低效果均无视技能免疫。","attrib":"施法延迟： <span class=\"attribVal\">1.67</span><br />\n移动速度减少: <span class=\"attribVal\">25%</span><br />\n攻击力降低: <span class=\"attribVal\">50%</span><br />\n减速持续时间： <span class=\"attribVal\">5.000000</span>","cmb":"<img src=\"mana\" alt=\"魔法消耗\" />魔法消耗:150/175/200<br /><img src=\"cooldown\" alt=\"冷却时间\" />冷却时间:120/110/100","lore":"那些死者的灵魂被捕获，用来毁灭他们生前的盟友。","hurl":"Shadow_Fiend"}],"itembuilds":{"Starting":["flask","tango","slippers","slippers","branches"],"Early":["magic_stick","boots","ring_of_aquila"],"Core":["magic_wand","power_treads","black_king_bar","tpscroll"],"Luxury":["invis_sword","assault","greater_crit","desolator","butterfly","monkey_king_bar","skadi"]},"skillup":[{"groupName":"常规加点","desc":"<p>1.在装备等级优势下可选择早点光环用来增大输出，否则还是黄点为主。<br />2.出门后1级选择N积累攻击力方便补刀，3级后有了2级Z、影压便可压制大部分的英雄，7级补满影压。前期如果能压中3段的话，伤害非常恐怖<br />3.由于SF大招需要积累足够的死灵，所以一般2技能满后才会选择升大，大招提供的减速技能是SF唯一的留人技能，8级后一般有大就要点。</p>","abilityKeys":["nevermore_necromastery","nevermore_shadowraze1","nevermore_shadowraze1","nevermore_necromastery","nevermore_shadowraze1","nevermore_necromastery","nevermore_shadowraze1","nevermore_necromastery","nevermore_requiem","nevermore_dark_lord","nevermore_requiem","nevermore_dark_lord","nevermore_dark_lord","nevermore_dark_lord","attribute_bonus","nevermore_requiem","attribute_bonus","attribute_bonus","attribute_bonus","attribute_bonus","attribute_bonus","attribute_bonus","attribute_bonus","attribute_bonus","attribute_bonus"]}],"hp":"agility","faction":"dire","name":"Shadow Fiend","name_l":"影魔","atk":"ranged","atk_l":"远程","roles":["Carry","Nuker"],"roles_l":["核心","爆发"],"nickname_l":["SF","Shadow Fiend"],"statsall":{"init_str":15.0,"init_agi":20.0,"init_int":18.0,"lv_str":2.0,"lv_agi":2.9,"lv_int":2.0,"init_hp":435.0,"init_mp":234.0,"init_armor":1.8,"lv_hp":19.0,"lv_mp":13.0,"lv_armor":0.14,"in